INSERT INTO `match_day_packages` VALUES (1,'THE DIAMOND SUITE','Designed to bring you closer to the game, the Diamond Suite delivers the ultimate VIP matchday experience, with exquisite dining in private luxury surroundings.',840,'1630857485LSY2bH.jpeg','EXPERIENCE AN UNFORGETTABLE MATCHDAY','<p>Our most premium matchday offering promises an entire day of entertainment in some of the most exclusive seats in the stadium. Your matchday experience begins in your private suite with Champagne on arrival, followed by an award-winning four-course fine dining experience before taking to your seats to watch the entertainment unfold on the pitch.</p>','2021-09-05 09:28:05','2021-09-14 09:12:34','1630857485Z6BJLv.jpeg',10,1),(2,'PLATINUM VIP TICKETS','Watch the match from the halfway line in the historic East Stand, in some of the best matchday seats that Stamford Bridge has to offer.',600,'1630866344GPsnod.jpeg','WATCH IN THE MOST PREMIUM SEATS','<p>Arriving two and a half hours prior to kick-off, your Platinum package includes luxury padded seating in the East Stand along with complimentary dining and drinks throughout the day. This is the ideal package for Chelsea fans or to entertain friends, family, colleagues or business associates for a special occasion.</p>','2021-09-05 11:55:44','2021-09-05 11:55:44','1630866344OqrwSo.jpeg',10,0),(3,'SILVER VIP TICKETS','A vibrant atmosphere and award-winning dining make this package the ideal option for hosting clients or enjoying a special occasion with friends and family, with seating and dining in the premium West Stand.',360,'16308665662pxfJR.jpeg','ENJOY GREAT SEATS AND RELAXED DINING','<p>For a more relaxed dining experience, our Silver VIP experience offers an exquisite four-course Chef&#39;s table with a variety of delicious options to choose from. Enjoy a whole day of entertainment on and off the pitch, with appearances by Chelsea legends, premium seating in the West Stand middle tier, award-winning dining, and a complimentary bar throughout the day.</p>','2021-09-05 11:59:26','2021-09-05 11:59:26','1630866566t3fJBv.jpeg',30,0),(4,'BRONZE VIP TICKETS','Enjoy a relaxed and informal dining setting with a pre-match appearance from a Chelsea legend, delicious award-winning food and match seating in the prestigious West Stand middle tier.',300,'1630866723GND69F.jpeg','TREAT YOUR FRIENDS AND FAMILY IN STYLE','<p>A bright and lively atmosphere and delicious three-course fine dining creates the perfect matchday experience for hosting clients, or treating friends and family to a full day of entertainment at Stamford Bridge. Arriving two and a half hours ahead of kick-off, you will be greeted by our dedicated waiting staff and enjoy a delicious meal before taking to your matchday seats to watch the action on the pitch.</p>','2021-09-05 12:02:03','2021-09-05 12:02:03','1630866723B4jn29.jpeg',50,0),(5,'THE HEALTH CLUB','Soak up the matchday atmosphere at London’s leading health club with a sumptuous pre-match three-course dining experience, before taking your seat to watch the action unfold.',240,'1630866873tQX3RJ.jpeg','THE HEALTH CLUB','<p>Soak up the matchday atmosphere at London&rsquo;s leading health club with a sumptuous pre-match three-course dining experience, before taking your seat to watch the action unfold. Seats located in the West Stand lower tier make this the perfect matchday with a difference.</p>','2021-09-05 12:04:33','2021-09-05 12:04:33','1630866873SQo9Zf.jpeg',100,0),(6,'FRANKIE’S SPORTS BAR','Soak up the pre-match atmosphere at the stylish and contemporary Frankie\'s Sports Bar at Stamford Bridge, ideal for sports fans wanting a lively pre-match experience with 16 big screen TVs and contemporary dining options.',240,'1630866993ofn77Q.jpeg','A TRUE CHELSEA DAY OUT','<p>Enjoy delicious pre-match a la carte dining and a complimentary bar in the relaxed environment that is Frankie&#39;s Sports Bar. Immerse yourselves in the day&#39;s pre-match live sport before taking your seats in the East Stand upper tier to finish off a truly unforgettable Chelsea matchday.</p>','2021-09-05 12:06:33','2021-09-05 12:06:33','1630866993KnQFKy.jpeg',100,0),(7,'THE 1905 CLUB','Named in honour of the year Chelsea Football Club was founded, the 1905 Club offers a premium matchday experience in stylish surroundings for the perfect combination of dining and entertainment.',240,'1630867115XGG4lT.jpeg','A LUXURIOUS MATCHDAY WITH THE FINEST DINING','<p>Contemporary and stylish, the 1905 Club provides the ideal package for entertaining friends, family or business associates in luxury surroundings at Stamford Bridge. Your VIP matchday experience includes Champagne on arrival, post and pre-match dining in your suite and a complimentary bar, giving you the complete hospitality experience. Your package includes luxury padded seats in the West Stand upper tier for a panoramic view of the stadium and the action on the pitch.</p>','2021-09-05 12:08:35','2021-09-05 12:08:35','1630867115yTw5k4.jpeg',100,0);
